{"tid":335258,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【惡女下場...】強國女大鬧新加坡機場 襲擊地勤判囚24天","createTime":"2017-07-25T12:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T16:05:42.000Z","uid":22675,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"240e6ecbcf168de805420aa8b56f296b9294548e","tid":335258,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:27:47.000Z","msg":"2017-07-25 09:23:12 HKT<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170725/large/1500944616_3800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170725%2Flarge%2F1500944616_3800.jpg&h=3f3b550a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據新加坡傳媒報道，一名中國女遊客常麗慧（33歲），上月11日晚上11時許到樟宜機場後，因無法在櫃位領取機票和登機證，在新加坡航空售票櫃台大吵大鬧，順手拿起標示牌襲擊地勤女職員，昨日被判入獄24天。<br />\n<br />\n案情透露，常女使用家人的信用卡預購了機票，事發當日，她到新航櫃位拿取機票並辦理登機手續時，將護照和信用卡交給地勤陳雪玉（30歲），不過陳雪玉發現護照和信用卡上的資料不一樣，於是詢問卡主是誰。常女稱，信用卡是她家人的，那個人在北京。<br />\n<br />\n由於陳雪玉無法確認信用卡持有人的身份，也無從證實持有人是否同意購買機票，所以沒有發出登機證給常麗慧。她建議常女通知信用卡持有人聯絡新航中國辦事處，確認他同意購票。常女氣憤地答說她沒有手機，也無法聯絡上該名家人，然後破口大罵。<br />\n<br />\n常女之後要求退款，當她得知要等上兩三星期才能取回退款時，更是怒火高漲，指着陳雪玉大罵。陳雪玉致電主管匯報情況時，常女隨手拿起桌上「櫃台關閉」的標示牌猛丟向陳雪玉的臉。陳雪玉痛得大叫，左眼眉毛處和鼻樑被割傷流血。庭上揭露，標示牌長約25厘米，寬6厘米。常女事後沒有道歉，立即轉身離開返回酒店，她隔天在酒店被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56998738&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56998738%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170725&d=ammElTl8ef0XgIZwl6iYvzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=50001f70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56998738%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170725&h=271b723a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56998738&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170725</a>"},{"pid":"bfd69645665d13875923ba98cf88e5ab4f0d726d","tid":335258,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:15:04.000Z","msg":"中國領屎館幫唔到手咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d2ad29527374d4fcce9d3e2d93462366b74ef8","tid":335258,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:18:36.000Z","msg":"個樣都好惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa915130cf3d6c2e152b6fd7c693878fc93d81d","tid":335258,"uid":100598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:22:27.000Z","msg":"如果個職員破左相咁就一世 條仆街要負責人地整容費用"},{"pid":"cbc73ffa99f23e3d4f86c7b1132013451d5cf5ed","tid":335258,"uid":43809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:25:37.000Z","msg":"判打藤啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc0a4cffcb7ee432cbd7fb9a8bf03f7086bd485","tid":335258,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65001a05050d42cfc288b9bc4fda448522deb3b9","tid":335258,"uid":37413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:31:27.000Z","msg":"打藤啦"},{"pid":"cf9d199e64df9bb10cffdb67f07be8922c99ca1e","tid":335258,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:31:39.000Z","msg":"傻西 緊係香港發啦 點解新加坡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474b0f671d5a0ccf96db0c0bd5bd4b2a319e41c3","tid":335258,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打藤啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不能同意更多"},{"pid":"93fbc088394698bf817a9fa0183bc619ac8b05ad","tid":335258,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:37:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傻西 緊係香港發啦 點解新加坡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港試過好多單用「誤會」了事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3885dd33d9dc62b4ee787fa881e35a626a7b257","tid":335258,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:42:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">欣賞一下香港既垃圾法官！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">國泰俏空姐航班上被支那八婆踢傷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170715/large/1500048154_c123.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170715%2Flarge%2F1500048154_c123.jpg&h=7c21d71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨午5時許，國泰航空一班回港的航班上，一名29歲姓溫空姐疑被一名34歲中國籍姓劉女乘客襲擊，踢傷腳部。事件驚動警方到場，於航機降落後處理，經調查後警員拘捕劉女，帶署調查。遇襲空姐需送院治理，幸經檢查後無大礙已出院。國泰航空則表示，事件已交警方處理，未能提供進一步資料，但強調該航班服務並無受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">違保釋條件嘗試出境　涉襲國泰空姐支那婦再獲法官批准保釋</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2017年07月21日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170721/56984252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170721%2F56984252&d=ammElTl8ef0XgIZwl6iYvzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=bfa80b34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170721%2F56984252&h=89d81697\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170721/56984252</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170721/large/1500620581_c53e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170721%2Flarge%2F1500620581_c53e.jpg&h=1873d79d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告劉曉曉 ( 資料圖片 )<br />\n<br />\n支那婦因涉嫌在國泰航機上推撞及踢傷囼泰空姐而被控普通襲擊罪，案件提堂後支那婦獲准保釋候訊，但不得離港。惟昨日傍晚她被發現於機場嘗試出境，即場被截獲，今被押上法庭。被告辯稱急往支那醫院為病父簽署文件，最終她再次獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n控方指，女被告劉曉曉（34 歲）昨天被發現在傍晚約 6 時半欲離港，被告今在法庭不停抽泣，解釋因父親患心臟病住院，「爸爸對我來說是在世上唯一的親人，對他很在意」，指昨日下午收到醫院來電，指其親在醫院要她立即簽字，院方亦將父親的照片及影片發給她，她已轉發在港朋友及律師。<br />\n<br />\n被告稱在港從未犯罪，不清楚法庭程序，不是有心違反命令。裁判官一度將案押後讓她冷靜及聯絡律師，再開庭時被告情緒明顯已平伏，不時用手掩着鼻子。而據律師庭上指，被告未婚，曾受高等教育及留學巴黎，是一名成功人士。  <br />\n<br />\n裁判官最終決定不撤銷其保釋，亦不打算要求她到警署報到，但將保釋金由3,000元加至8,000元。被告暫仍毋須答辯，押後至 8 月 28 日再訊，待控方進一步調查及索取法律意見。<br />\n<br />\n被告被指於本月 14 日，在一班由曼谷來港的航機內襲擊女子阮亦雯（29歲）。據知，兩人疑因收拾餐盤問題而爭執，空姐被人推撞及踢傷左腳。"},{"pid":"269a3b4007ca0d8713b93ab2c503d7468ddf4d85","tid":335258,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:42:32.000Z","msg":"香港法律界100%垃圾, 真係無呃你地的"},{"pid":"bff728a25a29c45c88fc814f2eb6f37c58c9199c","tid":335258,"uid":62402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:43:59.000Z","msg":"咁判都有嘅！？搞撚錯...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n判咁輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4ed88f59516514d56599fc3fc9c454279042d0","tid":335258,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:44:25.000Z","msg":"主權國家 同 殖民地 既分別<br />\n<br />\n仲永續乜鳩基本法既, 真係智商零"},{"pid":"49d20dbf304411dafcb10607f51ff6ca00e7e8db","tid":335258,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:44:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁判都有嘅！？搞撚錯...<br />\n<br />\n判咁輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輕得過香港班狗法官?"},{"pid":"acdf7ed37c09762443450052d9e3014d91e1f353","tid":335258,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:40:45.000Z","msg":"D大陸人 只會係香港機場搞事 先無事<br />\n<br />\n佢人係番自己中國機場搞事, 一樣比人打柒"},{"pid":"272f0563513d27b1c297d577001a4d4ef54c2e38","tid":335258,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:45:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打藤啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不能同意更多</blockquote><br />\n係囉，坐乜，打三藤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f791c7ca8bf32473e3f62b247e459258af8c2a06","tid":335258,"uid":56147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T16:05:42.000Z","msg":"信用卡儲緊分都唔敢幫 朋友買機票<br />\n<br />\n一執正就PK<br />\n<br />\n有次登機又係突然問我拎信用卡睇 (自己名)  果陣咁岩換新銀包<br />\n個心都離一離  無就真係唔洗上機"}]}